overview: The Gabba gang goes on a space adventure in a flying saucer. They look through a telescope at the stars and planets. In space they meet new friends and discover a new planet. The Gabba gang also experience different weather conditions, learn about machines, and care for the environment in various ways. Episodes include: Green, Space, Weather and Robot. Featuring alternative rock band - Jimmy Eat World.
title: Yo Gabba Gabba: Space Adventure
